      "version": "v2026.05.07.1",
      "releasedAt": "2026-05-07T07:47:28Z",
      "summary": "Modular tools + new Sound Effects tool",
      "description": "Start splitting tools into lazy-loaded modules and add a new Sound Effects tool with stackable processing and profile save/apply.",
      "changes": [
        "Add lazy tool-module loader for on-demand imports",
        "Add Sound Effects tool with Compression/Reverb/Visual EQ/Delay and per-effect toggles",
        "Support combined multi-effect processing in one chain",
        "Add Sound Effect profiles saved per user in Firebase",
        "Add manual Settings usage checker with collection counts and size estimates",
        "Expand GuitarPro accepted file formats and keep cloud-synced viewer settings"
      ]
